com.hygenics.crawler

Class BreakMultiple

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hygenics.crawler.BreakMultiple

  • public class BreakMultiple
extends Object
    Breaks apart Records with Multiple Entries. This may be the result of having run a looped or multiregex query. Also performs Replacements. This class works for one table. Utilizes split queries. I found that using the DAO template and bonepc pool has the same effect as pooling jdbc connections and running more connections.About ~22.4 seconds (22.35 average) for ~12000 posts and ~1000 pulls along with parsing using ~1700 regex operations, all with fork/join pools. Don't go too high. I swamped the server with connections. It hates me for a while.
    Author:
    aevans
